cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.SD

This paper presents a semi-supervised regression model based on deep learning and probabilistic modeling. The paper focuses on improving regression tasks using unlabeled data, which is a common problem in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) since these sub-categories are closely related to deep learning and regression tasks. Additionally, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SD (Software Engineering) are also possible sub-categories since the paper combines neural networks and Gaussian processes.
